OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FAn Italian court has reconvicted
OL,7,FAmanda Knox of slander, rubbishing
OL,8,Fhopes of removing a legal stain that
OL,9,Fhas marked her since she was
OL,10,Fexonerated of her roommates murder in
OL,11,F2007
OL,13,FAmanda Knox has failed to have her
OL,14,Fname cleared of a slander charge after
OL,15,Fwrongly accusing a Congolese man of
OL,16,Fmurdering her British flatmate while
OL,17,Fthey were exchange students in Italy.
