OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FMs Knox was convicted of the murder of
OL,7,FMeredith Kercher before being
OL,8,Fexonerated in a case that grabbed
OL,9,Fglobal attention and headlines.
OL,11,FHowever her accusation against Patrick
OL,12,FLumumba, who owned the bar where she
OL,13,Fworked, while being questioned by
OL,14,Fpolice over Ms Kercher's death landed
OL,15,Fher back in court this year.
OL,17,FIn 2016, the European Court of Human
OL,18,FRights ruled that the interrogation
OL,19,Fviolated her rights because she was
OL,20,Fquestioned without a lawyer or
OL,21,Fofficial translator.
