OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FBased on that ruling, Italy's highest
OL,7,FCassation Court threw out the slander
OL,8,Fconviction in November - nine years
OL,9,Fafter the same court overturned
OL,10,Fconvictions for Ms Kercher's murder
OL,11,Fagainst Knox and her Italian ex-
OL,12,Fboyfriend, Raffaele Sollecito.
OL,14,FBecause of this, and judicial reform
OL,15,Fin Italy allowing cases that have
OL,16,Freached a definitive verdict to be
OL,17,Freopened if human rights violations
OL,18,Fare found, the court ordered a new
OL,19,Ftrial.
