OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FMs Knox asked eight Italian judges and
OL,7,Fjury members on Wednesday to clear her
OL,8,Fof a slander charge.
OL,10,FShe told the court she wrongly accused
OL,11,Fan innocent man of the killing under
OL,12,Fintense police pressure in overnight
OL,13,Fquestioning without the benefit of a
OL,14,Flawyer or competent translator.
OL,16,F"I am very sorry that I was not strong
OL,17,Fenough to resist the pressure of
OL,18,Fpolice,'' Knox told the panel in a
OL,19,Fnine-minute prepared statement. She
OL,20,Ftold them: "I didn't know who the
OL,21,Fmurderer was. I had no way to know."
