OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FMs Knox showed no emotion as the
OL,7,Fjury's verdict that she was still
OL,8,Fguilty of slander was read out.
OL,10,FShe will not serve any more jail time
OL,11,Fas the four years she served before
OL,12,Fher murder acquittal counts towards
OL,13,Fthe three-year sentence for slander.
OL,15,FKnox, now a 36-year-old mother,
OL,16,Freturned to Italy for only the second
OL,17,Ftime since she was freed in October
OL,18,F2011.
